data.name: Swift Blade
data.description: This is Krolik's everyday outfit. Don't be fooled by those cute bunny ears; her sharp blade is what truly defines her.

data.name: Prancing Bunny
data.description: Simplified armor and lightweight clothing allow for greater agility. Krolik approves of this design, as long as it keeps the bunny ears.

data.name: Krolik's Training Outfit
data.description: Krolik's training attire. It lacks her beloved bunny ears, a fact that visibly annoys her. As a result, she pushes herself to the limit in every training session, eager to finish quickly and switch back to her preferred outfit.

data.name: Galaxy Interpretation
data.description: Nemesis' typical outfit. The night sky inscribes the path of the stars, but where is the astrologer's destiny written?

data.name: Nemesis' Training Outfit
data.description: Nemesis' training outfit. Although it's standard issue on the Elmo, the dark fabric makes Nemesis appear even more enigmatic

data.name: Serene Dark River
data.description: Soft clothing made from various materials. The crisscrossing lines resemble a winding dark river, enveloping Nemesis and blending into the night.

data.name: Wandering Star Trail
data.description: The outfit Nemesis wore while wandering in the contamination zones has a modern design with mysterious elements that are hard to decipher. When the paths of the stars change, where will they lead? With this outfit, Nemesis can move forward without any confusion.

data.name: Sweetheart Rescue
data.description: Often seen equipped with gloves, a hat, and a backpack, Colphne is always ready for a rescue mission!

data.name: Silent Heart
data.description: A present Colphne received from the Commander. It is a commonplace nursing Doll's uniform with a touch of personalization. Her clamorous thoughts have finally settled into blessed silence, and now what she must do is believe in her friends and that she is not alone.

data.name: Colphne's Training Outfit
data.description: Colphne's training attire features dark-colored clothing, which is unusual for Medical Dolls, so Colphne finds this quite novel.

data.name: Swift Messenger
data.description: Lenna's preferred attire, perfectly suited for both the silent infiltration of the night and the fierce clashes of frontline combat.

data.name: Flying Phantom
data.description: She hides her form and secrets in the night, protecting everything she loves with her silent guardianship.

data.name: Vitality Magic
data.description: A gift Lenna received from the Commander. Whether if it is a delicate flower or a playful bow – it finds a perfect home on Lenna.

data.name: Energetic Focus
data.description: Vepley’s outfit: Although her stage attire is not as dazzling as it once was, but her custom-made dinosaur backpack is still super cute!

data.name: Sparkling Wish
data.description: Vepley's idol outfit, her outfits during her idol activities are a kaleidoscope of adorable styles—playful, vibrant, and infused with a touch of local charm. Protecting everyone's smiles is Vepley's everlasting wish.

data.name: Summer Echo
data.description: This is Vepley's summer concert outfit. Her aqua dress sways with the beat like rolling waves, dancing in time to the music under the sapphire sky. Vepley will always bring the warmth of summer to the Commander.

data.name: Blade's Aegis
data.description: Groza typically wears a white trench coat that carries the flames of battle, serving as the beacon for the team's advance.

data.name: Dawn of Battle
data.description: The outfit Groza likes to wear when participating in important battles is adorned with falling stars along the hem. When the stars fade and daybreak arrives, it marks the moment of victory.

data.name: Groza's Training Outfit
data.description: Groza's training outfit makes her look sharp and capable. Upon getting closer, you can catch a faint fragrance, probably from the team leader's favorite detergent.

data.name: Sangria Succulent
data.description: The elegant design and cut, along with the slightly mysterious color, perfectly complement Groza's sophisticated temperament.

data.name: Dual Hunter
data.description: Peritya's typical outfit. The distinct footwear design enhances her agility.

data.name: Born Huntress
data.description: Peritya's sportswear. Light, slim-fitting and doused in bright, showy colors, it adds a touch of liveliness and energy to the otherwise languid Peritya.

data.name: Radiance Noctune
data.description: Sharkry's typical outfit. Even a proud little demon can't resist the allure of a cute bunny ear bow.

data.name: Swimsuit Idol
data.description:
"Commander, make sure you cheer for me at today's poolside concert, okay?♥”
She's all dressed up and ready to go, showing off her most perfect self in the water.

data.name: White Cosmos
data.description: Dushevnaya's typical outfit. A brave white knight naturally needs a black windswept cape.

data.name: Whimsical Military Uniform
data.description: The crisply pressed lines of Cheeta's military uniform confine a boundless wellspring of creative ideas.

data.name: Sparks on the Circuit
data.description: This is Cheeta's race queen outfit, a form-fitting but cool-looking outfit. In a race of speed, there is no need to adhere to the usual rules. She shall ignite the passion of racing with you.

data.name: Grey Meteor
data.description: Tololo usually wears a distinctive outfit, always carrying guns and cameras.

data.name: Celestial River at Dusk
data.description: Tololo's beachside outfit. The sea breeze teases its fabric and her silk camisole seems to blend into the Milky Way. The object of Tololo's gaze approaches her amidst the twinkling of the stars.

data.name: Winter Woods Walk
data.description: Nagant's typical attire is lightweight and warm, but the most crucial item is her hat, which boosts her confidence and provides a sense of security.

data.name: Summer Pitcher
data.description: While exploring the contamination zone, Nagant found a new outfit that suited her perfectly. This ball is filled with the love and care of her predecessors, so take it with gratitude!

data.name: Celestial Grace
data.description: Qiongjiu's outfit: A simple yet elegant outfit that represents professionalism and solemnity.

data.name: Flawless Hospitality
data.description: Spotless work clothes conceal Centaureissi's secret weapon: a gun belt strapped beneath. A great maid can not only brew delicious coffee but also serve as a dependable guard.

data.name: Charming Kitchen Chef
data.description: Sabrina's outfit: Black pepper and ketchup... Hmm, not referring to the colors of her clothes, but rather the ingredients for a certain kind of pasta.

data.name: Strawberry Zabaione
data.description: The fragrance of berries rests on the soft cream and sweet liquor. It is Sabrina's highly-recommended secret weapon for beating the heat; it's a unique piece of lovely scenery in the scorching summer winds even moreso.

data.name: Smoke Seeking
data.description: Daiyan's typical outfit features stylish cuts paired with flowing designs that highlight her refined taste.

data.name: Narcissus
data.description: The color scheme is as elegant as flawless jade, and the tailored fit accentuates the wearer's graceful curves.

data.name: Frost Field Snow Owl
data.description: Mosin-Nagant's outfit features a fur-lined coat and warm gloves, paired with a Northern Mule in the bitter winter—it's the perfect combo.

data.name: Caramel Melody
data.description: Makiatto's usual outfit. She rarely opens her violin case; it holds her most cherished weapon.

data.name: Ballroom Interlude
data.description: This is the dress that Makiatto wears to the ball. Its simple style, adorned with a familiar ribbon, carries a secret hope—that her dance partner will finally take notice of her.

data.name: Embroidered Bamboo, Blooming Shadows
data.description:
"—D-don't look at me, you d-dork."
Unfortunately, both her voice and face indicate that she's looking forward to this.

data.name: Pattering Rain
data.description: Jiangyu's outfit, meticulously chosen with colors that complement Daiyan's, creates a perfectly coordinated sisterly look.

data.name: Girl Hides Gold
data.description: Ksenia's typical outfit. The handbag she carries not only hides a gun but can also hold Sardis Gold.

data.name: Guiding Thornlight
data.description: Ullrid's outfit is thick, warm, and windproof, boasting unique patterns that blend function with flair.

data.name: A Serene Letter
data.description: Littara's everyday outfit features a hat with a star-shaped signal booster which facilitates message reception. In the wilderness, careful listening is more heartwarming than a thick fleece.

data.name: Snow Bright
data.description: Suomi's typical attire. A warm winter ensemble, naturally complete with a fur collar and fluffy pom-poms.

data.name: Sparkling Ocean
data.description: Suomi's beach attire. The vibrant ribbon design resembles a fish's tail, making Suomi the happiest pixie in the ocean as she wears it.

data.name: Earnest Defense
data.description: This is Papasha's usual outfit. The medal on her chest will shine forever, as a symbol of her deep-seated wish to protect her friends.

data.name: Spiritual Grass
data.description: Lotta's signature attire. An invocation of the vibrant grass; laying low yet holding a beauty of its own.

data.name: Athletics Rookie
data.description: Lotta's sportswear. Inconspicuous and usable in all sorts of sport competitions, it ensures Lotta's comfort and agility in exercise.

data.name: Leisurely Patroller
data.description: Andoris's usual outfit. With a rather unique design and tailoring, this outfit complements her gentle and accomodating temperament, yet possesses a futuristic sense of fashion.

data.name: Red Hot Bell Pepper
data.description: Faye's usual outfit. This clean cut of bright red makes her look like a bolt of leaping flame.

data.name: Raging Blaze
data.description: The graceful dancer, enveloped in a blazing energy, sweeps across the battlefield with a swiftness and ferocity to unsettle everything in her wake.

data.name: Concealment Gear
data.description: Vector's usual outfit. The discreet color scheme allows her to easily hide traces of her activity, allowing Vector to perpetually gain an advantage by always staying ahead in combat.

data.name: Molotov Bunny
data.description:
"Commander... What type of battle is this outfit even designed for? By the way... Did I just hear Ruchey scream?"
Vector refused to put on the bunny ear decorations on grounds of it interfering in combat.

data.name: Vivi Sometimes Hides Her Molotovs
data.description:
“I know I still have much room for improvement, Commander. If you have any suggestions, please feel free to tell me.”
Her eyes are sincere as she meets your gaze, yet there's a hint of worry in them.

data.name: Leaping Signal
data.description: Belka's usual outfit. A highly saturated high-contrast combat uniform ensures that her spirited figure is a presence on the battlefield that cannot be ignored.

data.name: Enchanting Imp
data.description: Belka's Halloween outfit. Slightly revealing, it makes the onlooker more embarassed than the wearer. This is all in the name of capturing the Commander's heart!

data.name: Clean Military Uniform
data.description: Springfield's usual outfit. The elegant colors bring out the regal qualities of the outfit, subconsciously inducing those around Springfield to treat her with respect. Her warm smile however, dissipates any sense of awkwardness or need for formality.

data.name: Queen in Radiance
data.description: She is more dazzling and eye-catching than any jewel under the lamplight. A single gentle smile from her was enough to capture the gazes of everyone in front of her.

data.name: S-Grade Cuisine Hunter
data.description: This is Qiuhua's everyday outfit. In keeping with her fiery nature, it's light and maneuverable, suited for handling woks and stoves so she can cook up a plate of "hope" for people in the direst of situations.

data.name: Drifting Cloud
data.description: Zhaohui's typical outfit. Her dark green sleeves flutter in the wind as she leaps, a streak of brilliant color that strikes fear into the hearts of her enemies.

data.name: Superspeed Chequer
data.description: This is Zhaohui's race queen outfit, a light and well-fitting set of clothes. The chequered flag sets hearts pounding as the hot wind blows across the track. Zhaohui looks toward the person approaching her and together, they join this wild celebration.

data.name: Dreamland War
data.description: Mechty's usual outfit. The weatherproof coat becomes a nice sleeping bag if you just wrap it around you...

data.name: Blazing Star
data.description: Klukai's usual outfit. Her ultramarine jacket is the most eye-catching sight on the battlefield, but Klukai has never been afraid of being the center of her enemies' attention — or rather, that was the aim of choosing her outfit in the first place.

data.name: Speed Star
data.description: This is Klukai's riding outfit. Her pure white bodysuit hugs her lovely curves. Like a zephyr or a tempest, this shining knight extends an invitation to you. Mount up, ride out!

data.name: Astral Luminous
data.description: Klukai's tactical rider outfit. It combines protective features with combat assisting capabilities, allowing Klukai to weave through the frontlines like a blue streak of lightning.

data.name: Fantasy Merchant
data.description: This is Peri's everyday outfit. Its eyecatching accessories complement her big-lensed glasses. Does this outfit make this newly-minted underground broker look a little cooler, perhaps?

data.name: Fashion Dancer
data.description: Yoohee's typical outfit. Youthful and energetic, dexterous and graceful. Not bound to a particular style, she's dedicated to delivering the passion of life to every audience.

data.name: Miracle Sweetheart
data.description:
"I'm going to enchant you with a spell of happiness next, Commander~"
Her eyes are filled with nothing but your presence, longing to see your smile.

data.name: Model Paragon
data.description: Nikketa's usual outfit. The spotless blue security uniform highlights her serious attitude towards justice: To be the nightmare of criminals, to be a paragon of those who protect the smiles of children.

data.name: Dance Like the Blazing Sun
data.description:
"Good luck! You can do it! Fight ON! This outfit is modified from the one I designed for the kids a long time ago. It bore witness to how the children grew up... and how I matured."
She dances like the blazing sun, inspiring people with her liveliness and tenderness.

data.name: Operation Pechenyan
data.description: 优雅如月，神秘似影。穿上强化作战服的佩里缇亚与阴影完美融合，化身追猎者将自身的野性释放。

data.name: Boundless Valor
data.description:
“每一次阅读诗文，赏析戏曲之时，心智总会被古人的情义与正气所触动。作为您的部下，我也希望我能像诗文中一般。”
不论天涯海角，纵使面对千军万马，她也绝不会背叛你的期待。

data.name: Siberian Slide
data.description:
“我所经历过的困难，如落雪寒霜……不过尔尔。”
她看向你的眼神中，从未有过阴霾，唯有对生活的淡然。

data.name: 理性凝望
data.description: 莱娅的常见着装。将独特的个性融入象征理性的制服设计之中，独行却不逾矩，这种矛盾对立的特质，正是莱娅独有的魅力。

data.name: Diamond Flower
data.description:
“和过去相比，我参加宴会的次数是越来越多了。不过，我最期待的那一场……至今都没有对我发起邀请啊，指挥官~”
她带有笑意的眼眸紧盯着你，似乎在期待你的回答。

data.name: 机械之心
data.description: 洛贝拉的常见着装。明艳大方的黄色与她冷淡的面容形成了极致的反差，但却也揭示了她的内心——柔软而包容，重视同伴超过一切。

data.name: Future Navigator
data.description:
“所谓英雄就是在黑暗绝境中开辟出光明之路的存在。”
她兴致高昂地看着你，眼里充斥着期待与信任。

data.name: 共沐日光
data.description: 莱妮的常见着装。相较以前变得更加清爽，或许是卸掉了一部分冗余数据，心智也随之变得更加豁然的原因吧。

data.name: Operation Butterfly
data.description:
“真是让人怀念的服装……不过现在想想我好像从来没有用这个姿态和指挥官好好自我介绍吧？机会难得，弥补一下？”
她拉着你的手，向你提出了那些年信件中未能实现的邀约。
